node.text:
This Hennessey Venom 1000 GT500 Mustang makes 859 rear wheel HP and 669 rear wheel lb-ft torque on our Dynojet chassis dyno using E85. This performance upgrade features a flex fuel tune that also supports 93 Octane.⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠⁠

This HPE850 performance upgrade is expertly installed and calibrated, supported by world class customer service, and guaranteed with a 2 year / 24k mile warranty.

Learn more: http://hennesseyperformance.com/vehic...​

Up your Z06 to 850 (or 1000!) HP with Hennessey:
979-885-1300 | http://www.HennesseyPerformance.com

node.title: 850 HP Hennessey Corvette Z06 // SIGHTS AND SOUNDS!
